industry. Specific objectives for local content issues are:
* Facilitating and developing local businesses and Tanzanians to participate effectively in the petroleum industry;
* Acquiring appropriate technology to enable Tanzanians to manage and operate the petroleum industry;
* Increasing the number of Tanzanians employed in the petroleum value chain;
* Facilitating establishment of maintenance service centres and strengthen local capacity in fabrication and manufacturing;
* social and economic  development of the Tanzanian Communities;
* Enabling Local Businesses and Tanzanians to access funding for supply of standard goods and services required in the petroleum industry; and
* Ensuring that Government and Tanzanians have sufficient capacity to participate effectively in the petroleum value chain.

The Government shall:
* Ensure targeted, objective based and transparent subsidy;
* Support capital investment subsidy for strategic energy infrastructure development;
* Facilitate implementation of lifeline tariff for customers with less ability to pay; and
* Ensure that petroleum prices to strategic projects and households are affordable and predictable.
